metadata.name: A Lezpire
metadata.description:
Part of the METAPRIDE LAND 2022 Collection

A Lezpire, 2022 is a 1/1 genesis piece preceding the upcoming mint of my generative collection, A Lesbian. The project aims to increase representation, visibility and the overall presence of the LGBTQIA+ community in web3 and beyond. The work itself is based on a series of self portraits that explore the concept of performing gender through pop culture, humor, and self examination. A Lesbian and A Lezpire both aim to spread love, laughs, awareness, and authentic connections between LGBTQIA+, BIPOC, WOMEN and ALLIES. A percentage of primary sales will go to the It gets Better Project, Outright International and the Fund for Grieving Children.
